    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/567a94fd05a1275516c99bcdb6deb3b8.webp?t=1732119247\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《借刀杀敌》是一款操作简单，快节奏的弹幕射击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一堆带有反抗精神的红色生物入侵了数据世界。而CANO则要击败他们。但是</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CANO没有双臂，或是魔法。因此，他需要利用自己的双脚奔跑引导敌人的武器来击杀敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >了解攻击方式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/40640b369fafb682c70d7e91116af4c0.poster.avif?t=1732119247\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/40640b369fafb682c70d7e91116af4c0.webm?t=1732119247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378300/extras/40640b369fafb682c70d7e91116af4c0.mp4?t=1732119247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动，引导武器击中敌人，但小心，同时也会对玩家造成伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败8个BOSS，便可借助它们的武器清理剩余力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-可随时存档。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-操作简单，只需移动和鼠标点击升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-较为不错的打击感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作说明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-WASD移动，鼠标左键购买升级项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
